.rule_1_9_2_ensure_local_timezone_is_properly_configured

Reference: al/asa-96-general-config/basic-hostname-pw.html

Remediation: 
Step 1: Acquire standard zone name (enterprise_zone_name) used by the enterprise
(GMT, UTC, EDT, PST)




Step 2: Run the following to configure the required value
hostname(config)# clock timezone <enterprise_zone_name> <local_offset>

.